<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q9_v3" title="Q9_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>El monto total a pagar por varias entradas se puede obtener sumando lo que cuesta cada grupo de entradas del mismo tipo (cantidad de entradas por precio de cada una).</p>
    <p>En un parque de diversiones se venden entradas con los siguientes precios:</p>
    <p>Una familia compra las siguientes entradas:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>2 entradas infantiles</li>
      <li>3 entradas de adulto</li>
      <li>1 entrada de adulto mayor</li>
    </ul>
    <div>
      <table border="1">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Tipo de entrada</th>
            <th>Precio (en pesos)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Infantil</td>
            <td>3000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Adulto</td>
            <td>5000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Adulto mayor</td>
            <td>2000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones permite calcular el monto total que paga la familia?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
         pesos
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esa expresión solo suma una entrada de cada tipo: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero la familia compra 2 infantiles, 3 de adulto y 1 de adulto mayor, por lo que el total debe considerar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
         pesos
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esa expresión calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Ese resultado no corresponde al monto total. El total correcto es sumar cada grupo de entradas: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2000</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
         pesos
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La expresión multiplica la cantidad de entradas de cada tipo por su precio y luego suma esos montos: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5000</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2000</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
         pesos
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esa expresión calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>42&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Ese valor no coincide con el monto total correcto, que es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la cantidad de entradas de cada tipo</strong></p>
            <p>La familia compra 2 entradas infantiles, 3 entradas de adulto y 1 entrada de adulto mayor.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el costo de cada grupo de entradas</strong></p>
            <p>Entradas infantiles:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entradas de adulto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entrada de adulto mayor:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Sumar los tres montos</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las expresiones dadas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión que representa exactamente ese cálculo es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>C</strong>, porque calcula por separado el costo de cada tipo de entrada y luego suma esos valores para obtener <strong>23 000 pesos</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>